HEADWORD: Supposal
<hw>Sup*pos"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
supposing; also, that which is supposed; supposition; opinion.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Interest, with a Jew, never proceeds but upon <qex>supposal</qex>,
at least, of a firm and sufficient bottom.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suppose</ent>⟦br⟧
